<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
  <title>情報検索台帳</title>

  <style>
    :root {
      --bg:#f4f6fa; --panel:#fff; --line:#d7dee8; --text:#1f2937;
      --sub:#667085; --accent:#1f6feb; --hover:#f8fbff;
      --selected:#eef5ff; --mark:#fff2a8; --danger:#dc2626;
      --shadow:0 2px 10px rgba(15,23,42,.06);
    }

    * { box-sizing:border-box; }

    html,body {
      margin:0; padding:0; background:var(--bg); color:var(--text);
      font-family:"Yu Gothic UI","Yu Gothic","Meiryo",sans-serif;
      font-size:14px;
    }

    body { min-width:1380px; }

    .page { width:96%; max-width:1800px; margin:18px auto; }

    .top-panel,.panel {
      background:var(--panel); border:1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius:14px; box-shadow:var(--shadow);
    }

    .top-panel { padding:18px 20px 16px; margin-bottom:16px; }

    .title-row {
      display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:end;
      gap:16px; margin-bottom:14px;
    }

    h1 { margin:0; font-size:28px; color:#0f172a; }

    .title-wrap p { margin:6px 0 0; color:var(--sub); font-size:13px; }

    .meta-box { text-align:right; color:var(--sub); font-size:13px; }

    .search-row {
      display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 110px 110px; gap:10px;
    }

    .search-row input {
      height:44px; border:1px solid #c8d2df; border-radius:10px;
      padding:0 14px; font-size:15px;
    }

    .btn {
      height:44px; border:none; border-radius:10px;
      font-weight:700; cursor:pointer;
    }

    .btn-search { background:var(--accent); color:#fff; }
    .btn-clear { background:#64748b; color:#fff; }

    .status-row {
      display:flex; justify-content:space-between; margin-top:10px;
      color:var(--sub); font-size:13px; min-height:24px;
    }

    .status { color:var(--accent); font-weight:700; }
    .error { color:var(--danger); font-weight:700; }

    .main {
      display:grid; grid-template-columns:560px 1fr; gap:16px;
      min-height:760px;
    }

    .panel { overflow:hidden; }

    .panel-header {
      padding:14px 16px; border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
      background:#fbfcfe; font-weight:700; color:#0f172a;
    }

    .list-toolbar {
      display:flex; justify-content:space-between; padding:10px 16px;
      border-bottom:1px solid #e7edf5; background:#fcfdff;
      color:var(--sub); font-size:13px;
    }

    .list-scroll {
      overflow-y:auto;
      height:calc(760px - 52px - 46px - 66px);
      background:#fcfdff;
    }

    .list-item {
      padding:14px 16px 12px; border-bottom:1px solid #e8edf4;
      cursor:pointer; background:#fff;
    }

    .list-item:hover { background:var(--hover); }

    .list-item.selected {
      background:var(--selected); border-left:4px solid var(--accent);
      padding-left:12px;
    }

    .item-title {
      font-size:16px; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:8px;
      color:#0f172a; word-break:break-word;
    }

    .chips { display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:6px; margin-bottom:8px; }

    .chip {
      padding:3px 9px; border-radius:999px; background:#eef2f7;
      color:#334155; font-size:12px;
    }

    .item-preview {
      color:#475467; line-height:1.7; white-space:pre-wrap;
      word-break:break-word;
    }

    .item-footer {
      margin-top:10px; font-size:12px; color:#667085;
      display:flex; justify-content:space-between; gap:12px;
    }

    .pager {
      display:flex; justify-content:center; align-items:center; gap:6px;
      padding:14px 12px; border-top:1px solid #e7edf5;
      background:#fbfcfe; min-height:66px;
    }

    .pager-btn {
      min-width:40px; height:36px; padding:0 12px;
      border:1px solid #cad5e2; border-radius:8px; background:#fff;
      cursor:pointer; font-weight:700;
    }

    .pager-btn.active {
      background:var(--accent); border-color:var(--accent); color:#fff;
    }

    .pager-btn:disabled { opacity:.45; cursor:default; }

    .pager-ellipsis { color:#94a3b8; font-weight:700; }

    .detail-scroll {
      overflow-y:auto; height:calc(760px - 52px); padding:18px 20px 24px;
    }

    .detail-title {
      font-size:24px; margin:0 0 14px; color:#0f172a; word-break:break-word;
    }

    .detail-grid {
      display:grid; grid-template-columns:170px 1fr; gap:10px 14px;
      margin-bottom:22px; padding-bottom:20px; border-bottom:1px solid #e6ebf2;
    }

    .detail-label { font-weight:700; color:#344054; }

    .detail-value {
      line-height:1.8; white-space:pre-wrap; word-break:break-word;
    }

    .detail-section { margin-top:20px; }

    .detail-section h3 {
      margin:0 0 10px; font-size:16px; padding-left:10px;
      border-left:4px solid var(--accent);
    }

    .detail-box {
      background:#fbfcff; border:1px solid #e6ebf2; border-radius:10px;
      padding:14px 16px; line-height:1.8; white-space:pre-wrap;
      word-break:break-word; min-height:56px;
    }

    .empty-box,.placeholder {
      padding:60px 20px; text-align:center; color:#667085; line-height:1.9;
    }

    mark { background:var(--mark); padding:0 2px; border-radius:2px; }

    a { color:var(--accent); text-decoration:underline; }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="page">
    <section class="top-panel">
      <div class="title-row">
        <div class="title-wrap">
          <h1>情報検索台帳</h1>
          <p>既存の SharePoint リスト情報を検索・閲覧するための専用画面</p>
        </div>
        <div class="meta-box">
          <div>対象リスト: <strong id="targetListName"></strong></div>
          <div id="targetListNote"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="search-row">
        <input id="keywordInput" type="text" placeholder="キーワードを入力（スペース区切りでAND検索）">
        <button class="btn btn-search" id="searchBtn" type="button">検索</button>
        <button class="btn btn-clear" id="clearBtn" type="button">クリア</button>
      </div>

      <div class="status-row">
        <div>表示件数: <strong id="resultCount">0</strong> 件</div>
        <div>
          <span class="status" id="statusText"></span>
          <span class="error" id="errorText"></span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="main">
      <div class="panel">
        <div class="panel-header">一覧</div>
        <div class="list-toolbar">
          <div id="pageSummary">0 件</div>
          <div id="pageInfo">0 / 0 ページ</div>
        </div>
        <div class="list-scroll" id="listArea"></div>
        <div class="pager" id="pagerArea"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="panel">
        <div class="panel-header">詳細</div>
        <div class="detail-scroll" id="detailArea">
          <div class="placeholder">
            左の一覧からデータを選択すると、<br>
            詳細内容がここに表示されます。
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <script src="./01-info.js?v=es5-1"></script>
</body>
</html>
